BAO CAO NGHIEP VU & CHUC NANG
QUAN LY KHACH SAN (Hotel Management)

1. GIỚI THIEU HE THONG
He thong quan ly khach san duoc xay dung theo mo hinh backend ASP.NET Core Web API va duoc luu tru tren SQL Server.
He thong ho tro cac nghiep vu tu le tan va quan tri, gom:
- Quan ly phong
- Quan ly khach hang
- Dat phong va kiem tra trung lich
- Nhan phong (check-in) / Tra phong (check-out) / Huy dat phong
- Ghi nhan dich vu phat sinh theo tung don / luu tru
- Xuat hoa don
- Audit log de theo doi cac thao tac


2. CAC VAI TRO (ROLES) VA QUYEN HAN
He thong su dung RBAC thong qua JWT va bang AppUser/AppRole/AppUserRole.

- ADMIN: quan tri he thong, thuc hien them/sua/xoa (xoa mem) cac du lieu chinh.
- RECEPTION: le tan, thuc hien dat phong, nhan/tra/huy, quan ly phong va tao khach hang.


3. DAT DIEM DU LIEU (DANH SACH THU PHAT SQL) VA TRANG THAI

3.1. Thuc the chinh
- Hotel (Khach san)
- RoomType (Loai phong)
- Room (Phong)
- Customer (Khach hang / dai dien)
- Guest (Thong tin khach thuc te o co the duoc gan vao Stay)
- Reservation (Dat phong - 1 reservation gan voi 1 phong)
- Stay (Lu tru thuc te sau check-in)
- StayGuest (Danh sach khach trong su lu tru)
- ServiceOrder (Danh sach dich vu phat sinh trong stay)
- Payment (Giao dich thanh toan)
- HousekeepingTask (Cong viec ve sinh)
- MaintenanceTicket (Phieu ky thuat)
- AuditLog (Nhat ky thao tac - audit)
- AppUser / AppRole / AppUserRole (Tai khoan & phan quyen)

3.2. Trang thai phong
Room.StatusCode:
- VACANT
- RESERVED
- OCCUPIED
- DIRTY
- CLEANING
- MAINTENANCE
- OUT_OF_SERVICE

3.3. Trang thai dat phong (Reservation.StatusCode)
- CONFIRMED
- CANCELLED
- NO_SHOW
- CHECKED_IN
- CHECKED_OUT

3.4. Trang thai lu tru (Stay.StatusCode)
- IN_HOUSE
- CHECKED_OUT

3.5. Trang thai dich vu phat sinh (ServiceOrder.StatusCode)
- ACTIVE
- CANCELLED

3.6. Trang thai thanh toan (Payment.StatusCode)
- PAID
- VOID

3.7. Trang thai ve sinh / ky thuat
- HousekeepingTask.StatusCode: OPEN / IN_PROGRESS / DONE / CANCELLED
- MaintenanceTicket.StatusCode: OPEN / IN_PROGRESS / DONE / CANCELLED


4. LUONG NGHIEP VU CHINH (END-TO-END)
4.1. Tai khoan va dang nhap
1) Nguoi dung dang nhap POST /api/auth/login.
2) He thong kiem tra username/password.
3) Neu hop le, he thong phat hanh JWT chua role code.
4) Cac API khac can phan quyen se kiem tra token theo JWT.
5) Neu dang nhap thanh cong/that bai, he thong ghi nhat ky vao bang `dbo.AuditLog` (Action: `AUTH_LOGIN_SUCCESS`/`AUTH_LOGIN_FAILED`, EntityName: `AppUser`, EntityId: username).

4.2. Quan ly phong
1) Xem danh sach phong (GET /api/rooms).
2) Them phong moi (POST /api/rooms).
   - Kiem tra HotelId ton tai va RoomTypeId thuoc Hotel do.
   - Kiem tra so phong khong trung trong cung Hotel.
   - Ghi nhat ky `dbo.AuditLog` (Action: `ROOM_CREATE`, EntityName: `Room`, EntityId: RoomId, AfterJson: thong tin phong).
3) Cap nhat phong (PUT /api/rooms/{id}).
   - Kiem tra RoomTypeId hop le trong Hotel.
   - Ghi nhat ky `dbo.AuditLog` (Action: `ROOM_UPDATE`, BeforeJson/AfterJson theo du lieu truoc va sau cap nhat).
4) Ngung hoat dong phong (DELETE - xoa mem):
   - IsActive = false
   - StatusCode = OUT_OF_SERVICE
   - Ghi nhat ky `dbo.AuditLog` (Action: `ROOM_SOFT_DELETE`, BeforeJson/AfterJson, reason: “Ngung hoạt động phòng (xóa mềm)”).

4.3. Quan ly khach hang
1) Danh sach khach hang (GET /api/customers).
2) Tao khach hang moi (POST /api/customers).
   - Validate du lieu dau vao (fullName, email, ...).

4.4. Dat phong va kiem tra trung lich
1) Tao reservation (POST /api/bookings).
2) He thong kiem tra:
   - Ngay check-out > check-in.
   - Phong ton tai va duoc phep dat (khong trong trang thai bao tru/out-of-service).
   - Khong trung lich voi reservation hop le:
     existing.CheckInDate < new.CheckOutDate
     AND existing.CheckOutDate > new.CheckInDate
3) Neu hop le:
   - Tao Reservation với StatusCode = CONFIRMED.
   - (Trong DB co SP) cap nhat trang thai Room = RESERVED.

4.5. Nhan phong (check-in)
1) Thuc hien nhan phong (PUT /api/bookings/{id}/check-in).
2) He thong kiem tra:
   - Reservation ton tai và khong bi CANCELLED.
3) Cap nhat:
   - Reservation.StatusCode = CHECKED_IN
   - Tao Stay (StatusCode = IN_HOUSE)
   - Cap nhat Room.StatusCode = OCCUPIED

4.6. Tra phong (check-out)
1) Thuc hien tra phong (PUT /api/bookings/{id}/check-out).
2) Cap nhat:
   - Stay.StatusCode = CHECKED_OUT, CheckOutAt = now
   - Reservation.StatusCode = CHECKED_OUT
   - Room.StatusCode = DIRTY (san sang cho ve sinh)

4.7. Huy dat phong
1) Thuc hien huy (PUT /api/bookings/{id}/cancel).
2) Cap nhat:
   - Reservation.StatusCode = CANCELLED
3) Kiem tra rang buoc theo nghiep vu (khong cho check-in sau khi cancel).

4.8. Dich vu phat sinh theo lu tru
1) Them dich vu cho booking/stay (POST /api/bookingservices).
2) He thong kiem tra:
   - Booking/Reservation ton tai
   - HotelService ton tai va hop le
3) Luu ServiceOrder:
   - Quantity, UnitPrice, LineTotal (so tien)

4.9. Xuat hoa don
1) Thuc hien xuat hoa don (POST /api/invoices).
2) He thong tinh:
   - RoomAmount = so ngay * RatePerNight (theo reservation)
   - ServiceAmount = tong dich vu ACTIVE (neu co)
   - TotalAmount = RoomAmount + ServiceAmount
3) Chi cho xuat hoa don sau khi booking/lu tru da CHECKED_OUT.

4.10. Audit log
1) Moi thao tac them/sua/ngung hoat dong/xoa mem co the ghi AuditLog.
2) AuditLog lu thong tin:
   - ActorUserId, Action, EntityName, EntityId
   - BeforeJson, AfterJson, Reason (neu co)
   - CreatedAt


5. CHUC NANG (FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS)
5.1. Auth - JWT
- Dang nhap bang username/password
- Phat hanh JWT
- Phan quyen theo role code
- Bao ve endpoint bang [Authorize]

5.2. Quản lý phòng (Rooms)
- Danh sach phong va bo loc theo:
  + roomNumber
  + statusCode
  + roomTypeId
- Lấy chi tiết theo RoomId
- Thêm phòng
- Cập nhật phòng
- Ngưng hoạt động phòng (xóa mềm)

5.3. Quản lý khách hàng (Customers)
- Danh sách
- Thêm mới
- (Goi y nang cap: sua/xoa mem/tim kiem theo SDT/CCCD)

5.4. Đặt phòng (Bookings / Reservations)
- Danh sách
- Tạo đặt phòng
- Check-in / Check-out
- Hủy đặt phòng
- (Goi y nang cap: endpoint tim kiem theo ngay, theo phong, theo trang thai)

5.5. Dich vụ (HotelServices và BookingServices)
- Danh mục dich vu (HotelServices)
- Them dich vu phat sinh theo booking (BookingServices)

5.6. Hóa đơn (Invoices)
- Danh sách hóa đơn
- Xuất hóa đơn khi booking da check-out

5.7. Dashboard / Báo cáo (Gợi ý)
- Ty le phong trong/da su dung
- Doanh thu theo ngay/thang
- Top dich vu su dung nhieu
- (Goi y: dung view / stored procedure de giam tai truy van)


6. API BACKEND (DANH SÁCH HIEN TAI)
Base URL: http://localhost:5066

6.1. Auth
- POST /api/auth/login

6.2. Rooms
- GET /api/rooms?roomNumber=&statusCode=&roomTypeId=
- GET /api/rooms/{id}
- POST /api/rooms
- PUT /api/rooms/{id}
- DELETE /api/rooms/{id}  (xoa mem / ngung hoat dong)

6.3. Customers
- GET /api/customers
- POST /api/customers

6.4. Bookings
- GET /api/bookings
- POST /api/bookings
- PUT /api/bookings/{id}/check-in
- PUT /api/bookings/{id}/check-out
- PUT /api/bookings/{id}/cancel

6.5. HotelServices
- GET /api/hotelservices
- POST /api/hotelservices

6.6. BookingServices
- POST /api/bookingservices

6.7. Invoices
- GET /api/invoices
- POST /api/invoices

Luu y: mot so endpoint co the chua co (toi uu) GetById/Sua/Xoa cho tat ca entity. Neu can, se mo rong theo MVP.


7. KIEM THU (TEST PLAN)
- Test JWT:
  + Login dung -> 200, co accessToken
  + Login sai -> 401
  + Gọi API khong token -> 401
  + Gọi API co token -> 200
- Test Rooms:
  + Them phong hop le
  + Them phong trung so phong
  + Them phong sai HotelId/RoomTypeId -> 400
  + Cap nhat phong
  + Xoa mem (ngung hoat dong)
- Test Booking:
  + Dat phong hop le
  + checkOut <= checkIn -> 400
  + trung lich -> 400
  + Check-in/check-out theo dung trang thai
- Test Invoice:
  + Xuat invoice khi checked-out -> 200
  + Xuat invoice khi chua check-out -> 400


8. HUONG PHAT TRIEN TIEP (FUTURE WORK)
- Bo sung endpoint CRUD cho Customers (sua, xoa mem, tim kiem theo SDT)
- Dung stored procedures DB de giam race khi dat phong
- Them AuditLog trong API (ghi before/after cho moi cap nhat)
- Bo sung module Dashboard va bao cao doanh thu (dung view)
- Hoan thien frontend (React/Angular hoặc Razor Pages) voi UI phân quyền theo role
- Them migration (thay EnsureCreated) neu chuyen sang EF schema management


KET LUAN
Tai lieu nay mo ta day du nghiep vu va cac chuc nang chinh cua he thong quan ly khach san, gan voi schema SQL Server va API backend.
Ban co the dung danh sach API va test plan de kiem chung nghiep vu truoc khi trinh bay do an.

